<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-15835] Upgrade-dtests on trunk not working in CircleCI</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15835</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;~3600 Upgrade-dtests are failing in CircleCI for trunk due to the missing &lt;tt&gt;JAVA8_HOME&lt;/tt&gt; environment variable.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patching the Docker image is rather simple by creating a new image:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
FROM nastra/cassandra-testing-ubuntu1910-java11-w-dependencies:20200406
ENV JAVA8_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-8-openjdk-amd64
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Pushed the above to Docker hub as &lt;a href=&quot;https://hub.docker.com/layers/snazy/cassandra-testing-ubuntu1910-java11-w-dependencies/202005261540/images/sha256-ac8a713be58694f095c491921e006c2d1a7823a3c23299e477198e2c93a6bbd7?context=explore&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;snazy/cassandra-testing-ubuntu1910-java11-w-dependencies:202005261540&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The size of the whole Docker image is a little concerning though (1.85G compressed), but that&apos;s out of the scope of this ticket.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll prepare a patch soon-ish.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
